# JOBFLOW .gitignore
# Personal data and runtime state MUST NOT be committed.

# ===== User data (gitignored entirely) =====
# Personal blueprints, answer bank, captured JDs.
user_data/
!user_data/README.md

# ===== Runtime state =====
queue.csv
*.log
server.log
server.err.log
.cron.log

# ===== Personal LaunchAgent plists =====
# The TEMPLATE in launchd/ is committed; only personalized installs (with usernames in the label) are ignored.
com.gregorio.*
*.plist
!launchd/*.template

# ===== Transient build artifacts =====
resume_manifest.js
build_samples.js

# ===== Output (resumes generated for the user) =====
output/
*.docx
*.pdf
# But DO commit assets like the logo
!assets/*.png
!assets/*.svg
!assets/*.jpg
!assets/*.webp
# And the GG_Resume_sample.docx is already deleted from the repo

# ===== System cruft =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# ===== Node =====
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json

# ===== Environment files =====
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example
